headline: United Airlines (UAL) Soars 14% on Optimistic Outlook, Ahead of Q2 Earnings
summary: United Airlines Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) is one of the stocks that are flying past expectations. United Airlines soared by 14.33 percent on Thursday to close at $91.67 apiece as sentiment was bolstered by upbeat comments about the overall travel industry and investor repositioning ahead of the release of its earnings results.
